quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,91,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí Allāhu sọ̀kalẹ̀.” Wọ́n á wí pé: “A gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí wọ́n sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún wa.” Wọ́n sì ń ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tó wà lẹ́yìn rẹ̀, òhun sì ni òdodo, tí ó ń fi ohun tó jẹ́ òdodo rinlẹ̀ nípa èyí tó wà pẹ̀lú wọn. Sọ pé: “Nítorí kí ni ẹ fi ń pa àwọn Ànábì Allāhu tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ tí ẹ bá jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo?"
  2,92,"Àti pé dájúdájú (Ànábì) Mūsā ti mú àwọn ẹ̀rí tó yanjú wá ba yín. Lẹ́yìn náà, ẹ tún bọ ọ̀bọrọgidi ọmọ màálù lẹ́yìn rẹ̀. Alábòsí sì ni yín.”"
  2,93,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí A gba àdéhùn lọ́wọ́ yín, A sì gbé àpáta s’ókè orí yín, (A sọ pé:) “Ẹ gbá ohun tí A fún yín mú dáradára. Kí ẹ sì tẹ́tí gbọ́rọ̀.” Wọ́n wí pé: “A gbọ́ (àṣẹ), a sì yapa (rẹ̀).” Wọ́n ti kó ìfẹ́ bíbọ ọ̀bọrọgidi ọmọ màálù sínú ọkàn wọn nípasẹ̀ àìgbàgbọ́ wọn. Sọ pé: “Aburú ni ohun tí ìgbàgbọ́ (ìbọ̀rìṣà) yín ń pa yín láṣẹ rẹ̀, tí ẹ bá jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”"
  3,31,"Sọ pé: “Tí ẹ̀yin bá nífẹ̀ẹ́ Allāhu, ẹ tẹ̀lé mi, Allāhu máa nífẹ̀ẹ́ yín, Ó sì máa forí ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ yín jìn yín. Allāhu ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  3,32,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀lé (ti) Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́. Tí ẹ bá sì pẹ̀yìn dà, dájúdájú Allāhu kò nífẹ̀ẹ́ àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́."
  3,33,"Dájúdájú Allāhu ṣa Ādam, Nūh, ará ilé ’Ibrọ̄hīm àti ará ilé ‘Imrọ̄n lẹ́ṣà lórí àwọn ẹ̀dá (àsìkò tiwọn)."